headline.print_headline: Official: 3 Dead, 1 Hurt in Maryland Air Crash
headline.main: Official: 3 Dead, 1 Hurt in Maryland Air Crash

lead_paragraph: An airplane and a helicopter collided in midair near a Maryland airport before crashing into trees Thursday, killing three men in the helicopter but sparing two in the plane who deployed a parachute to slow the aircraft's descent before it hit the trees.
